Week	Focus	Daily Tasks (1-2 Hours/Day)
Week 1	Jenkins (CI/CD)	- Day 21: Install Jenkins
- Day 22: Create a "Hello World" job
- Day 23: Build a pipeline for a Python script
- Day 24: Integrate GitHub with Jenkins
- Day 25: Deploy a static website via Jenkins
Week 2	Docker (Containers)	- Day 26: Install Docker
- Day 27: Run a pre-built Nginx container
- Day 28: Create a custom Dockerfile
- Day 29: Push an image to Docker Hub
- Day 30: Deploy a container on AWS EC2
Week 3	Terraform (IaC)	- Day 31: Install Terraform
- Day 32: Launch an EC2 instance
- Day 33: Automate S3 bucket creation
- Day 34: Destroy & rebuild infra
- Day 35: Store Terraform state in S3
Week 4	Projects + Resume	- Day 36: Build a CI/CD pipeline (Jenkins + Docker)
- Day 37: Automate AWS setup with Terraform
- Day 38: Update GitHub with projects
- Day 39: Optimize LinkedIn/Resume
- Day 40: Apply for 5 jobs/day
